## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible effects of crime on individuals. The data is limited to the information provided by the sources accessed, and there may be additional impacts not covered in this report. Furthermore, individual experiences of crime can vary widely, and the effects may differ based on personal circumstances and the nature of the crime.